{"tid":1146634,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《天才麻將少女》作者表明作品過半數角色是女同性戀孩子","createTime":"2019-05-09T10:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T02:40:56.000Z","uid":105678,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"23f0f35fec86bce2f509a0eec3614a6eb7bc6259","tid":1146634,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/04-14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F04-14.jpg&h=cf667954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2016年時作者小林立就曾在自家博客上清楚表明天麻登場的所有女性角色都是處女，連媽媽屬性的角色也是處女。<br />\n<br />\n都已是為人母親怎可能還是處女？難道《天才麻將少女》裡的媽媽全員都是&rdquo;聖母&rdquo;嗎？<br />\n為了解答這個疑惑，小林立最近就再次發文解說《天才麻將少女》的一些設定：<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/01-23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F01-23.jpg&h=8d79e0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關於作品角色的性取向，小林立表明包括已婚者，登場人物有半數以上是同性戀，有兩成是雙性戀，由於有iPS這樣的方法，超過一半的登場角色是女同性戀的孩子，《天才麻將少女》的世界是容許同性戀結婚的。"},{"pid":"d0ccd46096638d92f52995c880b4853ce776668a","tid":1146634,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b24